text: Arrow squid is a common name for a squid. Species called arrow squids include: 61 centimeter specimen of Slender inshore squid *Doryteuthis plei, the slender inshore squid *Heterololigo bleekeri, the spear squid *Nototodarus gouldi, Gould's squid *Nototodarus sloanii, the New Zealand arrow squid ==References== Category:Former disambiguation pages converted to set index articles Category:Squid
title: Arrow squid
